trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"></xref> object in the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 구성 요소 편집기를 제공는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"> </xref> 은 연결 된 개체 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> object in the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control at design time, under the control of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> object.
trans-unit.target: SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor 클래스 편집 하기 위한 사용자 인터페이스를 제공는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>의 요소는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>은 연결 된 개체 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>의 제어의 디자인 타임에 컨트롤의 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: There is a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: 한 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>연관는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>속성의는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>컨트롤.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> object is used to apply styles to static submenu items that depend on their level (nesting depth) in the menu structure.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>개체는 스타일 메뉴 구조에서의 수준 (중첩 수준)에 종속 된 정적 하위 메뉴 항목을 적용 하는 데 사용 됩니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor is invoked, for example, by selecting the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelSubMenuStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor가 호출 예를 들어, 줄임표 단추를 선택 하 여 (**... **)에 **LevelSubMenuStyles** 의 행은 **속성** 비주얼 디자이너의 모눈 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A> method always returns `false` to indicate that only one object can be selected at a time in the editor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>메서드는 항상 반환 `false` 를 나타내는 편집기에서 한 번에 하나의 해당 개체를 선택할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A> method creates a new form to display and edit the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>메서드가 표시 하 고 있는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> 편집 새 양식을 만듭니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A> method creates a new instance of the specified collection item type.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>메서드는 지정 된 컬렉션 항목 형식의 새 인스턴스를 만듭니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A> method returns an array of types that the editor can create.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>메서드를 편집기에서 만들 수 있는 형식의 배열을 반환 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> class when you select, for example, the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelSubMenuStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer when designing a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control or a control that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> class.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework는 내부적으로 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>클래스의 새 인스턴스를 생성을 선택 하면 예를 들어, 줄임표 단추 (**... **)에 **LevelSubMenuStyles** 의 행은 **속성** 비주얼 디자이너는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>컨트롤 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>클래스</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> 에서 파생 된 컨트롤을</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> 디자인할 때의 표</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the collection to edit.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>편집할 컬렉션의</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether multiple <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"></xref> elements can be selected in the editor at one time.
trans-unit.target: 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다 여부 여러 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"> </xref> 편집기에서 한 번에 요소를 선택할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The CanSelectMultipleInstances method always returns `false`; thus, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> object can be selected at a time in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> object.
trans-unit.target: CanSelectMultipleInstances 메서드는 항상 반환 `false`; 따라서이 하나만 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>개체에서 한 번에 선택할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new form to display and edit the current <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: 새 폼을 표시 하 고 현재 편집할 만듭니다 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"> </xref> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: The CreateCollectionForm method calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A> base method to create the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> form, and then formats a caption for the form.
trans-unit.target: CreateCollectionForm 메서드 호출의 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>기본 메서드를 만드는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>를 구성 하 고 폼의 캡션 서식을 지정 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm> to use as the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 인스턴스는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm>으로 사용 하 여 <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the specified collection item type.
trans-unit.target: 지정 된 컬렉션 항목 형식의 새 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: The CreateInstance method is used to create new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: CreateInstance 메서드는 새로 만드는 데 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: The CreateInstance calls the <xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A> method to access the activation methods for late-bound support.
trans-unit.target: CreateInstance 호출은 <xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A>에 런타임에 바인딩된 지원에 대 한 정품 인증 방법을 액세스할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Activator.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the item to create.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>만들 항목의 합니다.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A new instance of the specified type, which should be <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 있어야 하 고 지정 된 형식의 새 인스턴스 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the data types that this collection editor can create.
trans-unit.target: 이 컬렉션 편집기를 만들 수 있는 데이터 형식을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> object can create <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> type objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>개체를 만들 수 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>개체를 입력 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: A type array of the data types the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"></xref> can create.
trans-unit.target: 배열 형식의 데이터 형식에서 <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref> 만들 수 있습니다.
